The,human,translation,API,provides,direct,interface,to,more,than,professional,translators,and,over,languages,There,is,no,need,to,login,upload,files,etc,and,your,text,will,be,sent,directly,from,your,content,management,system,and,you,ll,get,the,translated,text,back,The,API,is,especially,useful,for,customers,with,high,volumes,of,content,such,as,financial,firms,new,media,companies,advertising,agencies,commercial,blogs,ecommerce,sites,and,other,content,generators,The,Human,Translation,API,is,currently,used,by,content,management,systems,web,sites,ecommerce,platforms,mobile,applications,and,more